Title: Ships in the Night
Plot: Gibbs and the NCIS team partner with a Coast Guard Investigative Service (CGIS) Agent to solve the murder of a Marine gunned down on a dinner boat.
GuestStars: Diane Neal, Roark Critchlow, Tiffany Dupont, Tyler Hynes, Patch Darragh, Gino Anthony Pesi, Leith M. Burke, Wes Brown
